		.igeLoading.content
			#headline.row
				.col-lg-12
					h2 We aware of the game performance issues and are
						| working actively to find a long-term solution!
			#mail-list.row
				.col-lg-12
					h2
						| Stay in the loop! Subscribe to the&nbsp;
						a(href='http://eepurl.com/VwFT5', target='_blank') Cosmos email list
						| &nbsp;to hear about game updates and events.
			#news.row
				#new-features.news.col-lg-3
					h2 New Features
					ul
						li See&nbsp;
							a(href='http://blog.teamleonine.com/?p=591', target='_blank') Cosmos
								| Version 0.16.0
							| .
				#improvements.news.col-lg-3
					h2 Improvements
					ul
						li Deconstruction is implemented! In construction
							| mode, click on your ship&#39;s blocks to instantly
							| deconstruct them!
				#bug-fixes.news.col-lg-3
					h2 Bug Fixes
					ul
						li None.
				#known-issues.news.col-lg-3
					h2 Known Issues
					ul
						li Ships are still drawn even after they have relocated
							| out of the viewable area.
						li Keyboard input does not work in Safari in fullscreen
							| mode.
						li Fullscreen mode is broken in Internet Explorer.
						li Game performance drops dramatically when many
							| lasers are fired.
						li Very large ships cause performance issues for all
							| players.
						li Occasionally, drops are not collected and placed in
							| inventory.
						li View the full list of known issues&nbsp;
							a(href='http://blog.teamleonine.com/?p=761', target='_blank') here
							| .
			#loading-error.error An error occurred while loading the game. Please refresh the page
				| or try again later. If the problem persists, email us at&nbsp;
				a(href='mailto:team@teamleonine.com', target='_blank') team@teamleonine.com
